Class DataBaseAccess

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.bohdatabase.DataBaseAccess

  • public class DataBaseAccess
extends java.lang.Object
    Database access for our local shared preferences of saved Characters This also handles deletion, update, and creation of this. (Built as a singleton instance to avoid multiple edits at once)
